Gyarados (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
This article lists each primary appearance of Gyarados in the Trading Card Game. For the deck archetype based around Gyarados, see Gyarados archetype (TCG).
← #0129: Magikarp
Pokémon
#0131: Lapras →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Gyarados (TCG Pocket).

Gyarados has been featured on 41 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Gyarados cards are normally Water-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Gyarados

Gyarados
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
